Robert Jr and Bellarmine Chatunga Mugabe are known for their lavish lifestyle and expensive night life. In the latest video to hit social media, Bellarmine Chatunga is seen pouring champagne from a bottle of Armand de Brignac, an expensive champagne, over his watch. The Mugabe sons made headlines recently when their mother‚ Grace Mugabe‚ assaulted a South African model‚ Gabriela Engels‚ she found in their hotel in Sandton. Engels opened an assault case but the Zimbabwean first lady was subsequently granted diplomatic immunity.